{
  "groups": [
    {
      "end": 14.131,
      "id": "p0",
      "index": 0,
      "section_index": 0,
      "section_kind": "weather_opening",
      "segments": [
        "s0"
      ],
      "start": 10.0,
      "text": "It is currently 19 degrees and cloudy in Berlin-Tempelhof."
    },
    {
      "end": 17.849,
      "id": "p1",
      "index": 1,
      "section_index": 1,
      "section_kind": "news_bridge",
      "segments": [
        "s1"
      ],
      "start": 14.131,
      "text": "With the morning weather set, here is the news."
    },
    {
      "article_ids": [
        "a4f166443dc",
        "a51c4003d1f"
      ],
      "end": 37.266,
      "id": "p2",
      "index": 2,
      "section_index": 2,
      "section_kind": "news",
      "segments": [
        "s2",
        "s3",
        "s4"
      ],
      "start": 17.849,
      "text": "The industry is establishing a new baseline for autonomous AI agents. The NVIDIA Blackwell Ultra NVL72 has taken the lead in AgentPerf, the first benchmark designed to measure agentic AI systems. This hardware performance is critical because AI agents have fundamentally changed the complexity of inference workloads."
    },
    {
      "article_ids": [
        "abf07a5ab4b"
      ],
      "end": 55.443,
      "id": "p3",
      "index": 3,
      "section_index": 3,
      "section_kind": "news",
      "segments": [
        "s5",
        "s6",
        "s7"
      ],
      "start": 37.266,
      "text": "These high-performance models are already moving into specialized security roles. Microsoft Research's Project Ire used an LLM agent to identify a LOTUSLITE malware specimen. The system produced a detailed behavioral report on the sample, detecting threats that most major endpoint detection tools missed."
    },
    {
      "article_ids": [
        "ad0b1e4ed9b",
        "a0a7e70a7a4"
      ],
      "end": 81.056,
      "id": "p4",
      "index": 4,
      "section_index": 4,
      "section_kind": "news",
      "segments": [
        "s8",
        "s9",
        "s10"
      ],
      "start": 55.443,
      "text": "While security agents target malware, other tools are focusing on the development and diagnostic process. Hugging Face and AllenAI released olmo-eval, a workbench that lets developers track how changes to data or architecture affect model performance. In the medical field, Google Research is exploring how AI tools can help laypeople understand skin conditions to bridge the gap before a professional diagnosis."
    },
    {
      "end": 83.948,
      "id": "p5",
      "index": 5,
      "section_index": 5,
      "section_kind": "weather_return_bridge",
      "segments": [
        "s11"
      ],
      "start": 81.056,
      "text": "After the headlines, back to the weather."
    },
    {
      "end": 91.797,
      "id": "p6",
      "index": 6,
      "section_index": 6,
      "section_kind": "weather_closing",
      "segments": [
        "s12"
      ],
      "start": 83.948,
      "text": "This afternoon will be cloudy with rain chances up to 85 percent and temperatures between 16 and 20 degrees."
    },
    {
      "end": 95.102,
      "id": "p7",
      "index": 7,
      "section_index": 7,
      "section_kind": "closing",
      "segments": [
        "s13"
      ],
      "start": 91.797,
      "text": "And that's it for your personal morning broadcast."
    },
    {
      "end": 101.712,
      "id": "p8",
      "index": 8,
      "section_index": 8,
      "section_kind": "signoff",
      "segments": [
        "s14"
      ],
      "start": 95.102,
      "text": "[mature adult voice, intensely emotional, tender, radiant; hold a long breath after Rise] Rise... and shine."
    },
    {
      "end": 112.453,
      "id": "p9",
      "index": 9,
      "section_index": 8,
      "section_kind": "signoff",
      "segments": [
        "s15"
      ],
      "start": 101.712,
      "text": "[very very long pause before speaking; then mature adult voice, most emotional, strong, warm, radiant, deeply encouraging; hold a long breath after Rise] Rise... and shine."
    }
  ],
